<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.7">
<l>mikka perumpukaḻ māvali vēḷviyiṟ</l>
<l>takkati taṉṟeṉṟu tāṉam vilakkiya</l>
<l>cukkiraṉ kaṇṇait turumpāṟ kiḷaṟiya</l>
<l>cakkarak kaiyaṉē yaccōvaccō</l>
<l rend="indent">caṅka miṭattāṉē yaccōvaccō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O He whose hand [bears] the discus,</l>
<l>who poked with a bit of straw the eye of Śukra</l>
<l>who forbade the gift saying, “this is not proper,”</l>
<l>at the sacrifice of Māvali of very great fame, Oh! Oh!</l>
<l>He with the conch on his left side! Oh! Oh!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
